    "description": "<strong><i>您可以通过在Steam上购买完整版来支持我们。完整版包含3个章节。</i></strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239820/extras/c0edcbf9661804a8732d00dbbbbc0574.poster.avif?t=1726319069\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239820/extras/c0edcbf9661804a8732d00dbbbbc0574.webm?t=1726319069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239820/extras/c0edcbf9661804a8732d00dbbbbc0574.mp4?t=1726319069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>游戏剧情：</strong><br>肖恩·特纳前往边远小镇——兔窟镇探望女儿。当肖恩抵达那里的时候，他察觉到某些坏事已然发生。小镇里没剩几个活人，废弃的大街小巷布满了可怕的怪物。肖恩必须尽快解救女儿，然后逃离这个人间炼狱。但是他很快就意识到，这里还隐藏着更多不可告人的秘密，而他要对抗的邪恶势力，出于某种原因，正在逐渐侵蚀我们的世界。<br><br><strong>游戏内容：</strong><br>随着充满谜团的冒险之旅不断推进，令人震惊的离奇事件层出不穷，肖恩也逐渐了解到镇民们的可怕秘密。在这一过程中，你会造访许多氛围十足的场所，解决形式多样的谜题，在各种危险怪物的进攻下逃出生天。剧情环环相扣，让你身临其境，进而体会到生存恐怖游戏的精髓。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239820/extras/3760bf00df9762c81a384536a75d919a.poster.avif?t=1726319069\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239820/extras/3760bf00df9762c81a384536a75d919a.webm?t=1726319069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239820/extras/3760bf00df9762c81a384536a75d919a.mp4?t=1726319069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>游戏特色：</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>剧情引人入胜，如同一部恐怖佳片。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>以氛围浓厚的小镇为背景，内含多栋可探索建筑物。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>画质诱人，场景细节丰富。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>各种怪物靠视觉和听觉对你穷追不舍。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>战斗方式多样，既能正面硬刚，又能潜行暗杀。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>无数的谜团和谜题等你去解开。</li></ul>",
